232
00:16:59,490 --> 00:17:00,680
Menyampahnya!

233
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:04,860
[ Vila Belia ]

234
00:17:02,310 --> 00:17:05,085
Sebab itulah kita tak patut berjumpa lagi!

235
00:17:29,810 --> 00:17:31,354
Profesor.

236
00:17:32,180 --> 00:17:34,084
Ada masalahkah dengan bahan kajian itu?

237
00:17:35,130 --> 00:17:37,775
Kalau awak beritahu apa yang kurang,
saya akan...

238
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:43,105
[ Universiti Myungil,
Yeo Jun di Festival Musim Bunga. ]

239
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:49,045
Dia abang saya.
